	<h2>About</h2>
	<p>
	I currently work at the Institute for Linguistics at the University of
	Stuttgart. Before this, I was a postdoc in the project <a
	href="https://wuegaki.ppls.ed.ac.uk/mecore/">MECORE</a> at the University of
	Konstanz (2021&ndash;2024). And before that, I was working on my PhD
	at UMass Amherst (2021).
	</p>

	<p>
	<!-- this paragraph should go before the first one-->
	I specialize on the semantics and the syntax of attitude reports. I'm
	also interested in event semantics and in how intonation interacts with
	meaning.
	</p>

